Ŵanthu ŵanandi awo ŵakucita vinthu vya mu ciyowoyero ici ŵakucita vinthu vinyake.
Ŵanthu ŵakutemwa kuŵa maso pa usiku wa Paska kuti ŵawone umo dazi likuŵalira.
Nangauli pali fundo zinyake izo Ŵakhristu ŵakusambizga pa nkhani iyi, kweni vingaŵa kuti likaŵa kaluso ka kukarwa kwa vula na kupambika.
Matchalitchi agho ghali na vigomezgo vinandi ghakuŵa na Ciraliro ca pa Sabata pa Sabata, ndipo mipingo kanandi yikuŵa na viphikiro para kwaca usiku kuti yikumbukire kuwuka kwa Yesu.
Vinyama vyose ivyo vikamba kukhala pa virwa ivi vikamba kuskamba, panji kuwuluka.
Chifukwa chakuti nyama izi zikaŵa kutali na charu, zikakwananga yayi kwenda, ntheura nkhumba zikuruzikuru zikaŵa nyama yakuliska chomene ku Galapagos.
Ŵanthu ŵakati ŵiza mu Galapagos, ŵakasangamo vinyama vinandi nga ni mahachi, ng'ombe, mbunda, mphumphi, ntcheŵe, na mbeŵa.
Para mwafika ku Antarctica panji ku Arctic mu nyengo ya chiwuvi, mukondwenge na usiku wa ku North Pole, apo zuŵa likuleka kunjira.
Iyi ni nyengo yiwemi comene yakuwonera dazi, cifukwa mtambo uzamuŵa mdima nyengo yose.
Pakuti ŵanthu ŵanandi ŵakuwona yayi malo agha, nyengo zinyake mungakondwa na nyenyezi.
Mu Japan, ŵanthu ŵakucita milimo yawo mwakuyana na umo ŵanthu ŵa ku vyaru vya kumanjiliro gha dazi ŵakucitira.
Ŵantchito ŵanyawo ŵakucemana na mazina ghawo panji mazina gha nchito.
Kugwirizana mu nchito nkhwakuzirwa comene, cifukwa cikung'anamura kuti ŵanthu wose ŵakutemwana, m'malo mwa munthu waliyose payekha.
Kanandi ŵantchito ŵakukhumba kuti ŵafumu ŵawo ŵaŵawovwire pa chilichose icho ŵakuchita, ndipo ŵakukhazga kuti ŵapulikirenge ivyo ŵafumu ŵawo ŵakuŵaphalira kwambura kususkika.
